high_descs: turn towards your left and go to the wall
turn right and go towards the kitchen table
pick up the closest knife with a yellow handle
turn to your right
turn back to the table and to the right again
carry the knife across the room to the stove
open the microwave and place the knife inside it
shut the microwave door and return to the kitchen table
pick up a potato slice from the table and carry it to the microwave across the room
cook the potato slice and the knife (!!!)
carry the cooked potato slice to the left side of the kitchen table
place the potato slice on the table between the sponge and the yellow handled knife
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of potato on the table

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room and then turn right to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife in the middle of the kitchen table.
Step to the right to face the potato on the kitchen table.
Cut the potato on the kitchen table into slices.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the microwave above the stove.
Place the knife in the microwave and shut the door.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the microwave above the stove.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the kitchen table.
Place the heated potato slice on the back of the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it on the back of the kitchen table.

high_descs: While facing the wall, turn to your left and walk toward the window, hang a right to the table.
Pick up the middle of the three knives nearest and to the left of the apple on the table.
Turn to your right in the direction of the green recycling bin, and turn back to the table.
Slice the potato in front of the loaf of bread.
Turn to your right and carry the knife to the stove.
Look up to the microwave oven above the stove.
Open the microwave door, place the knife in the microwave, close the door.
Turn to your right and walk back to the table.
Pick up a center slice from the potato, turn and walk back to the stove.
Look up to the microwave, open the door, put the slice behind the knife, turn the microwave on; after the microwave finishes cooking, open the door, remove the potato slice, close the door.
Turn to your right and walk to the left side of the table.
Place the potato slice in front of and to the right of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, microwave a slice, put the slice on the table
